{
  "stem": "7177.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And there was a conference in our living room, my parents sitting on the sofa.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Excuse me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "My father decided it was good for us to leave.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We did have people who would hide us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we did-- and he gave my brother-- I still remember him saying, you take care of the girls.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "You go.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We had-- we had a forest not far away from us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "You take the girls to the forest, you stay there overnight.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And don't-- tomorrow morning, at 5 o'clock by the time it gets a little bit lighter, go to this farm where you can make a phone call, and then you can go to your hiding place.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We-- for us to get out of the house after 8 o'clock, after the curfew, the danger was just as-- you know, the danger was right there.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We could have been picked up by German soldiers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because at that time, we did have hundreds of German soldiers in what used to have been-- what used to be a-- what should I say?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A gathering place of-- well, not nuns, but what-- [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What do you call them?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Friars.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they had taken those religious gentlemen out of there, and the Germans had taken that building.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So there were plenty of Germans around.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we were very, very fortunate.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It took us about five, 10 minutes before we got to the ground of the castle that was in our little town.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And from there, since we of course knew-- we used to walk, and hike, and do everything.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We knew our way around so well, we were able to go through the forest and end up in a barn where we knew there was a wagon.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "A horse and wagon.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
